Temple will allow a user to "pray" for certain stats. When the player is on the screen and has selected a stat, a timer will tick until adding a point to the chosen stat. The choices are strength, speed, vitality, endurance.
At game start, it should take 1 minute per stat. There will be modifiers that make this faster later on (piety being one of them). More points of said stat should slow down the next point gain.
When praying for a stat, display a progress bar with amount of time left until the point is achieved. Preserve this bar if the user leaves the screen and later returns.